# AI-hiring-assistent
# TalentScout Hiring Assistant

An intelligent chatbot designed to assist in the initial screening of technical candidates. Built with Streamlit and OpenAI's GPT model.

## Features

- Interactive chat interface
- Systematic collection of candidate information
- Dynamic technical question generation based on declared tech stack
- Context-aware conversation handling
- Secure data handling

## Installation

1. Clone the repository
2. Set up environment variables:
   ```bash
   export OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here


  Configured Streamlit Server to run streamlit run app.py --server.port 5000
